message.body: Check your email
OK
Really,$100.00.How will be paid?
Check, but it will probably take a month or two
How do I sign into the new email I don't have a password
You need to check that new email every once and awhile because you will be sent paperwork to get paid to that new address
I gave you the password in the email
Sorry, I didn't see it at first.thanks for your patience
No problem
looking at my activity on the website where do I see 2000 text donated?
I don't need to do anything anymore right as far as donating text it's automatic
Forgot to tell you I think you're eligible for new phone if you need it.
I checked with my boss, the texts are still being processed. The report will come out in a day or two with the new uploads and I can confirm the number of texts
But I think it said you successful donated 2015 messages. Not every one of those will be useable but most of them will.
Great,thanks
You are done. Just check that email I made for you in a couple weeks
My phone still works so I'll keep it for now
Study is still on for a while right?
A week or two longer
Finally got to target and picked up simply balanced coconut water.tried with mango peach flavor got to tell U it tastes a lot better than the plain & has 4 more g of sugar
If you like it great, but I think you should get the plain coconut water because even a little less sugar would be better for you
But it will help you stay hydrated either way
I saw they also carry coconut flour.wonder the health benefits of that.
Don't know
Did you even try the plain target brand coconut water?
No, just figured it would taste like the one I had from Weg's
They are all different I swear. Next time just get one of the plain ones from target, just to try it, you can mix it with the mango juice one if you don't like it.
But it's good, and better for you to drink the plain one.
Yeah I was thinking about getting the plain one in mixing if I didn't like it
You should be cutting back on sugars wherever you can
Lief said that 20 mins of cardio exercise a day will really help you to control your sugar levels
Not to mention your blood pressure
It has helped mine a lot since I started running again.
And it's only been like a week
I walk the dog minimum half mile daily & Will be trying to ride my bike after I pick it up today from SUE
Also drink the coconut water really cold, with ice cubes is good too
Will do!
